column3: About 20 kids in traditional clothing and hats waiting on stairs; a house and a green wall with gate in the background; a sign saying that plants can't be picked up on the right;

a rock hole in the ground surrounded by sand; one man in a white tee-shirt, grey pants and a white cap is holding a shovel, the other one is wearing black pants, a white jumper and a traditional hat, is walking towards him;
a yellow building with white columns in the background; two palm trees in front of the house; cars parked in front of the house; a woman and a child are walking over the square;

a large building on the left, a palm tree in centre of picture, (mostly) white cars in the street at a junction, some of them turning left, others going straight; there are red umbrellas in a park on the right; people are walking through the park, others are crossing the road in the foreground;
a white, large statue with spread arms on a hill; picture taken from behind; bushes and small trees on the hill; street leading up the hill; there are white clouds in the blue sky;
View of a city with many dark green trees and white houses with red roofs; there are a few high-rise buildings and a stadium in the centre;
a cascading waterfall in the middle of the jungle; front view with pool of dirty water in the foreground;
a man in a red tee-shirt and a woman carrying a red bag are watching some waterfalls on a lookout in the foreground; green trees, black rocks and a grey sky in the background;
View of giant, thunderous waterfalls over a u-shaped cliff; white clouds in a blue sky in the background;
a long dam with high voltage pylons; a blue sky with white fleecy clouds in the background;
two light brown church towers with pinnacles on all four sides; the left tower with windows, the right tower also with a clock; the artful central nave is a bit darker and has a cross on top;
View of an old town of a city with its colourful buidings and two churches from one of its alleys in the shade; the towers of the churches are still in the sun, the rest in already in the shade;
a white and blue church, with only the two towers in the sun, the rest in the shade; view from the side, with the old town of a city in the background;
against-the-light photograph of a beach at sunset; some clouds in the sky; there are people at the beach and palm trees in the background;

against-the-light photograph of a large, grey building with many arches and columns and a small tower with pinnacles; the Paraguayan flag is waving on top of the building; there are dark palms in the foreground and a blue sky in the background;
steam ship in a lake, docked; the flag of Paraguay at the bow of the ship; a blue sky in the background;
a grey building with many columns and arches and the modern high-rise buildings of a city with a blue sky in the background;
a black steam engine with one wagon; trees in the background;

Four locals are sitting on a bench in a canteen kitchen, leaning on a red brick wall; the three women are wearing skirts, wests and hats, one of them is holding a yellow plastic bag; the man is wearing trousers, a shirt and a cap;
Against-the-light photograph of a gate in the shade, with towers to its left and right; there are dark trees in the foreground and a blue sky in the background;

well exposed front view of the cathedral in Asuncion; two towers with flags, three arched entry gates, large central ave with several pinnacles and a cross on top; there is a clock on the right tower; streetlamps at the middle gate and at the corners; bells visible in both towers;
a fountain and cobbled walkway in the foreground, a pink and white buidling with many arches in the background; trees on the right;

a white building with lots of columns and arches, a neat lawn and neatly cut trees and bushes in the foreground; the flag of Paraguay is waving at the top of the building; there is a flower bed on the left;
a very modern building; stairs are leading up to the entrance; the walls are entirely made of glass; one red huge column is supporting the big roof; rails in the foreground; a green tree on the left;

two lane street with large shops on the right and smaller shops on the left; people are walking on the sidewalk, some are crossing the street; cars are parked along the left side of the street as well;
an avenue with seven yellow taxis lined up on the right side; some drivers are waiting for customers outside of their taxis; green trees behind them;
a swimming pool with sun chairs on a terrace in the foreground; a flat landscape with green trees and houses in the background;

Several flagpoles with waving flags on a green lawn in the foreground; a large grey and black building behind it; a huge column with a football on top on the left; a blue sky with white clouds in the background;
Front view of a huge dam; water is flowing through one tiny spot; backwater is flowing off on the left; green reed in the foreground;
Rock singer wearing yellow pants and a red T-shirt on a stage; view from behind; crowd is cheering in the background;

Two adults and four local boys are standing in front of a white house with two trellised windows; three boys are standing, one is kneeing down; adults are holding shoulders of boys; one boy is holding a sweeper;
Nine children, some of them waving at the camera, others are a bit shy and are looking away; one person is pointing to the camera;
Construction site, bare brickwork; one worker is standing on rails, the other one is leaning against an unfinished brick wall;
Close up picture of the Itaipu Dam; backwater is flowing off in the foreground;
two men are standing on a lawn in front of a light brown house with blue corners;

School kids on a grey square, some are dressed in dark blue, others in orange; one person dressed in orange is standing opposite the line up, leading the group; two light blue houses behind them with a steep hill in the background;
a woman is sitting at table in the middle of a schoolyard; there are many books on the table; two people are sitting next to her, six others are standing about ten metres away from the table;

four boys, one drinking from a cup, one wearing an army cap and waving, the one in the focus wearing a beanie, a jumper and smiling into the camera, and the fourth wearing a cap and carrying a wooden crate;
four school kids are smiling into the camera in the foreground; more kids in the background, some are leaning on the school wall, others are running around;
Young girl wearing a red trainer with blue and white sleeves is bending down to two old ladies; one of them is stroking the girl's face with her right hand;
five women in a kitchen, two of them are preparing some food using four bowls, two are standing behind them (and one next to them) and are watching;
Santa Claus in middle of excited kids; a woman with a present in the background;

Three social workers and about ten local kids in a room with dark and light blue walls; one of the workers is sitting and talking to the kids; the other two are just arriving or listening; one kid is a bit left out, sitting alone on a desk and looking the other way;

two tourists, both of them wearing backpacks, are visiting a school with ten pupils; the woman is wearing brown shorts and a yellow sleveless top; the man is wearing long black pants and a blue shirt;
some of the pupils are looking at them; brick walls and windows in the background;
A school kid is sitting at a desk, smiling into the camera and being offered a red apple; three other kids in the background;

Four tourists are sitting on a bus; two women in the front row with their heads turned around; another one in the second row looking out the window; and one man with sunglasses in the very last row, looking out the window too;

A tourist group is visiting a school; the school kids are sitting at their desks, singing a song and clapping their hands, with their teacher clapping as well; six of the tourists are standing behind them and are watching them, one tourist is taking a photo;

Three women are sitting on a wooden bench in front of an about one metre high, red brick wall; they are all wearing skirts and jumpers with gilets; two of them are wearing a hat too; one man is standing behind the wall; a wooden door on the left is being held open by a red brick;

photo of a classroom with some kids sitting at their desks, others standing at their desks, waving into the camera, laughing; two kids are eating their lunch in the foreground; there is a wooden wall with pictures of two comic figures in the background;
a large, black plastic bag with four packs of pasta, a folder, a leaflet, a small book and cacao powder on a table; there is a second, empty table in the background;

six kids are sitting around a table and playing with toy cars; one kid is standing next to the table; a woman is holding a black plastic bag on the left; three tourists in the background are talking to each other;
panorama view of houses in La Paz; red roofed houses in the foreground, with a hill and rugged rocks in the background;
photo of eleven school kids and three tourists behind them; a basketball court in the background, with one kid standing below the basket; a large mountain in the distant background;

Lots of locals (both kids and adults) in front of a blue building; one kid is about to slide down the slide, with one grown up waiting to catch it; another woman is carrying a basket in her left hand, with a kid holding her other hand; others are just sitting around or are standing in the background; there are snow covered mountains in the distant background;

there are two social workers in the foreground; one wearing a red pullover and brown pants is bending over to access the blue paint; the other one in a red tee-shirt and black jeans is watching her; at the back of the room there is another worker wearing a white tee-shirt and blue jeans, acutally painting; there are many newspapers on the ground to protect the kindergarten floor; all three workers are wearing a mask;
portrait of two dark-haired girls with a mountain in the background;
a man is carrying a heavy rice bag; a car on the left, another man on the right; a street behind them, with some houses on a hill in the background;

Six tourists are standing in front of blackboard of a primary school; one tourist is taking a photo; local kids are sitting at their desks, singing and clapping; one kid has just opened one book; there are posters and pictures on the wall in the background;
a little red wooden desk and two red and two blue chairs in front of a green wall full with children's paintings; an improvised cupboard with lots of drawers in a corner at the back of the room;

volunteer workers help with the construction in a kindergarten; four volunteers are squatting down and are trying to prise the ground with hammer and chisel; movable wooden walls are leaning on the wall in the background;

tourists are posing in a room, ten of them are standing, one is squatting; one kid is posing with them, five other kids are sitting at a table and eating out of three bowls; there are posters and pictures at the wall behind the tourists;
Pupils are sitting at their wooden desks in an open air classroom; two of them raising their hands, others smiling; three are wearing a green hat; red brick wall and windows in the background;

Seven tourists are visiting a classroom; children are sitting at round tables, nearly all of them wearing a green hat (except for two kids); tourists are smiling at the kids; there are posters and maps on the wall in the background;

Tourists are visiting an old people's home; each tourist is leading one old lady, arm in arm; the old ladies are wearing traditional dresses and a hat; the room is decorated with balloons; there is a picture on the wall in the background, and also an old lady carrying a green balloon;
a destroyed house with the wreckage lying around in front it; three ordinary a bit elevated houses in the background;

Six pupils are sitting around a round table on wooden chairs, each of them is holding a fruit (tangerine?) and is wearing a hat (except for one kid); pictures and comics on the wall behind them; car tyres in the background on the right;

a teacher and around 50 pupils on the slope of a hill; half of the kids are dressed in orange, many of them wearing a hat, a beanie or a cap; small bushes and two trees at the top of the hill; a lake in the background;

School kids are posing for the camera in a football-like setup - nine are standing at the back, ten are squatting at the front; each of them are having a fruit in their hands, most of them are smiling, one is even waving at the camera; a blackboard in the background; one kid in the centre of the front row is holding a teddy;

classroom with most of the pupil sitting at theirs desk and wearing green hats; one girl is standing at her desk, another one is walking to her desk, three other boys are standing and looking at a picture of Minnie Mouse on the wall; shelves and posters in the background;

children are sitting at their desks, together with a tourist sitting in the last row; three children are standing on the left, looking at a map of Peru;there are two posters on the wall at the back, and there is a bookshelf with a lot of boxes and folders on the left;

One boy holding a white box, most likely a present from the volunteer kneeing in front of him; several kids are around him, looking at the box while the boy himself is looking somewhere else; one kid in the foreground is wearing a green hat; there are both round tables and wooden desks in the background;

a volunteer, squatting down and browsing through a school book; school children around her, looking at the book too; in the background there is a table with school equipment on it; the kid in the foreground is holding a pencil;

tourists are standing in front of the blackboard in a classroom, all the kids are sitting at their desks; there is a clock above the blackboard, and also the letters "Dios es amor" between the clock and the blackboard, and "higiene es salud" on the side wall below the windows;
a boy wearing a green jacket and a red cap is carrying a little girl on his back;
